# Buy, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Buy () is a rural locality (a selo) in Bichursky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 659 as of 2010. There are 6 streets.
Geography
Buy is located 34&nbsp;km east of Bichura (the district's administrative centre) by road. Sloboda is the nearest rural locality.
